WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.220 --> 00:00:04.210
Birinchi qadamimiz foydalanish uchun 
ko‘rinishlarni tanlab olish haqida.

00:00:04.210 --> 00:00:08.290
Avvalo, men Android view o‘zi aslida 
nimaligini tushuntirib o‘tishim kerak.

00:00:08.290 --> 00:00:12.400
Sodda qilib aytganda, view ekranda biror 
narsani ko‘rsatib turuvchi to‘rtburchak.

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:15.610
U dastur tasvirlaydigan 
biron rasm, matn,

00:00:15.610 --> 00:00:17.170
tugmacha yoki shunga o‘xshash 
nimadir bo‘lishi mumkin.

00:00:17.170 --> 00:00:22.780
Alohida ko‘rinishlar birgalikda ekran 
layout(joylashuv)ini tashkil qiladi.

00:00:22.780 --> 00:00:24.690
Dasturda siz ko‘radigan va 
interfaol ta’sir qiladigan 

00:00:24.690 --> 00:00:29.120
barcha narsa foydalanuvchi interfeysi
yoki qisqa qilib UI deb nomlanadi.

00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:32.910
Ko‘rinishlarning bir nechta turlari bor.

00:00:32.910 --> 00:00:35.620
Matn ko‘rsatuvchi view 
 TextView deb nomlanadi.

00:00:35.620 --> 00:00:37.490
Mana unga misollar.

00:00:37.490 --> 00:00:41.540
Biron rasmni tasvirlovchi view ImageView 
deb nomlanadi. Mana unga ham misollar.

00:00:41.540 --> 00:00:45.070
Tugmachani ifodalovchi view 
 Button deb ataladi.

00:00:45.070 --> 00:00:46.620
Bular unga misollar.

00:00:46.620 --> 00:00:49.910
Hozirda, Android da ko‘rinishlarning foydalanish 
uchun ancha qulayroq turlari ham bor, 

00:00:49.910 --> 00:00:53.020
lekin biz quyida aytib o‘tilgan uchta 
turiga e’tiboringizni qaratmoqchimiz.

00:00:53.020 --> 00:00:55.770
Sal oldinroq har bir view bu ekrandagi 
to‘rtburchak ekanligini aytib o‘tdim, 

00:00:55.770 --> 00:00:57.890
lekin bu barcha to‘rtburchaklar 
qayerda joylashgan?

00:00:57.890 --> 00:01:01.290
Texnik jihatdan ular ko‘rinmas, ammo 
men siz uchun ularni chizib chiqaman.

00:01:01.290 --> 00:01:03.390
shunda siz har bir to‘rtburchakning 
tomonlari qayerda ekanligini ko‘ra olasiz.

00:01:03.390 --> 00:01:05.730
Ko‘rib turganingizdek,

00:01:05.730 --> 00:01:10.250
har bir dastur interfeysini shunday 
alohida ko‘rinishlarga ajratish mumkin.

00:01:10.250 --> 00:01:13.690
Ramziy ma’noda, view bu dasturda 
layout binosini qurish uchun guvala.

00:01:13.690 --> 00:01:16.150
Viewning ekranda to‘rtburchak bo‘lishini

00:01:16.150 --> 00:01:20.080
tushunishingizga yordam berishi uchun

00:01:20.080 --> 00:01:22.840
sizga ehtimol tanishroq bo‘lgan 
holatni keltiraman.

00:01:22.840 --> 00:01:26.110
Agar siz Paint yoki Google Drawingsga 
kabi dasturlardan foydalangan bo‘lsangiz,

00:01:26.110 --> 00:01:31.130
unda matn qo‘shish uchun TextBox dan 
foydalangan bo‘lishingiz mumkin.

00:01:31.130 --> 00:01:32.710
matn yozgan paytingizda uning tomonlari ko‘rinadi, 
biroq tashqi sohasiga bosganingizda 

00:01:32.710 --> 00:01:36.280
tomonlari yoqoladi, lekin ular joyida qoladi.

00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:39.090
Qachonki siz orqa fon uchun 
rasm qo‘yishni 

00:01:39.090 --> 00:01:41.260
yoki ular bo‘ylab chegara 
tortish kabilarni boshlaganingizda

00:01:41.260 --> 00:01:45.380
ushbu tortburchak kattaligi 
ahamiyatga ega bo‘ladi.

00:01:46.598 --> 00:01:51.100
Men view nomlarining camel case deb nomlanuvchi 
formatiga ham alohida e’tibor qaratmoqchiman.

00:01:52.240 --> 00:01:56.140
Ushbu qoidaga ko‘ra so‘zlar 
bir-biridan bo‘sh joy bilan emas

00:01:56.140 --> 00:01:58.860
bosh harflarining katta qilib 
yozilishi bilan ajratiladi.

00:01:58.860 --> 00:02:02.000
Bu nomlash qoidasi camel case 
deb atalishiga sabab

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:05.540
so‘z ko‘rinishi tuyaning orqa o‘rkachiga 
o‘xshab tepa-past bo‘lishida.

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:09.299
Bu kurs doirasida nomlashda camel case 
qoidasidan foydalanish tavsiya etiladi.

00:02:10.310 --> 00:02:12.420
Xo‘sh, keling endi o‘rganganlarimizni 
amalda sinab ko‘raylik.

00:02:12.420 --> 00:02:16.660
Bu Inbox deb nomlanadigan, Google tomonidan 
yaratilgan yangicha email dasturining skrinshoti.

00:02:16.660 --> 00:02:19.380
Bu yerda siz foydalanilgan ko‘rinishlarning 
turlarini aniqlay olasizmi?

00:02:19.380 --> 00:02:22.430
Sizga yordam sifatida alohida ko‘rinishlarni 
ajratib ko‘rsatib qo‘yganman.

00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:23.270
Misol uchun A,

00:02:23.270 --> 00:02:26.880
bu TextView , ImageView yoki 
 Button ligini ayta olasizmi?

00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:29.350
B uchun ham shu mashqni bajaring,
shuningdek, qolgan ko‘rinishlar uchun ham.

